title: Aurora. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: July 7th, 2015

Description:

In 2020, super-computer Kronos concludes that human beings are the biggest threat to the planet. 60 years later, Andrew finds himself lost in a world run by machines when he meets Calia, a girl on the way to a place called Aurora.

Director: Robert Kouba

Writers: Robert Kouba

Actors: Carmen Argenziano, Eileen Grubba, Julian Schaffner, Jeannine Wacker, Pavlo Bubryak

Genre: Romance, Science Fiction, Thriller

Run Time: 1 hour 47 minutes
